{"id":93353,"type":1,"name":"かりん","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f6/3a/93353_AA1eJ.jpg","rating":{"total":7,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":1,"7":3,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.7},"summary":"椎八場市に住む女子高生・真紅果林には、人に言えない秘密があった。それは、自分が吸血鬼一家に生まれた事だ。幼い時から吸血鬼の何たるかを教えられて育ったが、なぜか血が増える増血鬼として覚醒してしまう。吸血鬼の弱点全てが通用しない代わりに、特殊能力が全く使えない為、「落ちこぼれ」として兄や妹に馬鹿にされる憂鬱な日々を送っていた。\r\nある日、彼女が通う学校に雨水健太という少年が転校してきた。彼を一目見た途端、果林の胸が大きく脈打った……。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>增血鬼果林</li><li><span>册数: </span>14</li><li><span>话数: </span>58</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/9758\">影崎由那</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/7659\">長鴻出版社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7842\">富士見書房</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>月刊DRAGON AGE、<a href=\"/person/8377\">月刊ドラゴンエイジ</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2003年5月号</li><li><span>结束: </span>2008年3月号</li>","collection":{"wish":8,"collect":11,"doing":3,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"校园","count":2},{"name":"少女漫画","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1},{"name":"恋爱","count":1},{"name":"轻小说","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":9758,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/46/18/9758_prsn_711AL.jpg","name":"影崎由那","desc":"作者"},{"id":7842,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8d/6e/7842_prsn_1ff71.jpg","name":"富士见书房","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7659,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b9/fe/7659_prsn_lIzw0.jpg","name":"长鸿出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8377,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/27/fd/8377_prsn_Xzhn1.jpg","name":"月刊Dragon Age","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":10180,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f6/58/10180_LakjL.jpg","title":"かりん","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/10180"},{"id":94312,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ff/f8/94312_SeIY8.jpg","title":"かりん 増血記","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/94312"}],"comic":[{"id":94287,"name":"かりん (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b0/41/94287_jp.jpg"},{"id":94290,"name":"かりん (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/31/d8/94290_jp.jpg"},{"id":94291,"name":"かりん (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/65/b5/94291_jp.jpg"},{"i